:"Place prawn meat, mushrooms and strained liquid into mixing bowl and cook <b>5-8 min\/90°C\/\/speed 1<b> or until prawns are just cooked."},{"content":"Add tomatoes and cook <b>2 min\/90°C\/\/speed 1<b>. Divide between serving bowls and garnish with coriander just before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Please refer to the <i>Basic Cookbook<\/i> or the <i>Everyday Cookbook<\/i> for the Chicken stock paste recipe.","Shrimp paste (also known as belachan) can be found at Asian food stores or at some major supermarkets in the international aisle."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","45m","4 portions"]}